com.siperian.mrm.workflow.activevos2

Class AvosTaskData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.mrm.workflow.activevos2.AvosTaskData

  • public class AvosTaskData
extends Object
    This class represents a specific task's data. This is the data passed back and forth between ActiveVOS and the BDD to keep track of the workflow process context.
